---
title: Paneer and Black Bean Naan with Mango Chutney, Green Pepper and Potato Wedges
description: We love good Paneer and Black Bean Naan and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/paneer-and-black-bean-naan-c650176c-9f38c92f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/paneer-and-black-bean-naan-5d55582644341b00094a8478-d074d7cf.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/paneer-and-black-bean-naan-5d55582644341b00094a8478
